<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-10-17 13:40 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2651 &Cx1f; taf-z
u w &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-CONGRESS-105TH-NYT &LR;      10-17 1214
